Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:36.51,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}本格的な鬱の日差しが肌をこぼしていくように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:36.51,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}正如炎炎烈日倾洒在肌肤上一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.71,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:45.48,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}私もあなたに恋に焦がれる　海へドライブ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:45.48,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我也在去海边兜风的时候对你一见钟情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:49.07,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}運転する横顔慣れる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:49.07,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}习惯了你开车时的侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:52.86,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}潮風が気持ちいい Summer day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:52.86,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}夏日的海风 清爽心怡的 Summer day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:55.99,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}LA LA LA SUMMER DAY
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:55.99,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}LA LA LA SUMMER DAY
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:00:59.53,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}ビッチバレーするカラフルなウェア
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:00:59.53,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}沙滩排球时五颜六色的装束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:21:40.69,Warning,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.78,0:01:03.25,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}砂浜に咲く花みたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.78,0:01:03.25,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}就像在沙滩上绽开的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:05.50,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}Kiss you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:05.50,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}Kiss you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.62,0:01:08.92,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}あなたの心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.62,0:01:08.92,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}其实我真的好想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:13.26,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}もっと　もっと　近くに感じたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:13.26,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}更近 更近的感受你的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:16.05,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}私だけ見て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:16.05,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}请只注视着我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:19.43,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}Kiss you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:19.43,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}Kiss you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.64,0:01:29.94,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}服と膨らんだ胸の思い唇に乗せて伝えたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.64,0:01:29.94,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好想将那满胀的思念之情用双唇传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.06,0:01:31.69,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}だから Kiss you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.06,0:01:31.69,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}所以要 Kiss you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.86,0:01:33.32,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}だから Kiss you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.86,0:01:33.32,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}所以要 Kiss you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.65,0:01:37.57,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}だからさ　kiss you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.65,0:01:37.57,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}所以呀 我要 Kiss you
